project_descr:
The overall goal of the programme is to promote gender equality and women’s empowerment through strengthening capacities in the government, civil society and communities.
http://mptf.undp.org/factsheet/fund/JGE00

outputs.output_descr: The Joint Programme aims at advocating women’s increased participation in the policy making process and empowering them economically, thus setting up sound mechanisms for political and economic activism to collectively advance the gender equality agenda and to promote women’s political and economic empowerment at national and grassroots levels.
